                    <expan><abbr>Χ</abbr><ex>ριστὸ</ex><abbr>ς</abbr></expan> προσδέξ<lb break="no"/>ηται τὴν
                    δέησι<lb break="no"/>ν αὐτοῦ· ἀμήν.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>Our most pious John, the presbyter, slept and came to rest on July 30th,
                    indiction 12, and lies here. And may the Lord Jesus Christ receive his
                    supplication. Amen.</p>
